title: This Beautifully Renovated 2x2 Coming Available 08/29! Call For Deets
posting_body: ['11301 3rd Ave NE, Seattle, WA 98125', 'Row on Third Apartments in Seattle, WA Row on Third Apartments is ideally located in the center of the growing Northgate neighborhood of Seattle.', 'The community is tucked away near the beautiful Hubbard Homestead Park and just minutes from numerous dining and shopping venues.', 'Enjoy the convenience of being located along I-5 and the new Northgate Light Rail Station where you are minutes from Downtown Seattle.', 'Give us a call today to find out why you will love calling Row on Third your new home!', 'Apartment Features:', 'Spacious Floor Plans', 'Studio, 1-Bedroom & 2-Bedroom Homes', 'Ample Storage Space', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Vinyl Flooring', 'Brand New Finishes', 'Community Features:', 'Secured Building Access', 'Dog Run', 'Co-Working Space + Meeting Rooms', 'Zero Deposit Community', 'Located Near North Seattle College', 'Public Transportation Options Nearby', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
